      "module_path": "catalogue_lint_workflow",
      "docs": "Concrete implementation of RunCatalogueLint. Modify from baseline: per D17, the evaluation logic moves from InMemoryCatalogueLinter (infrastructure) to domain::evaluate_catalogue_lint (pure function). Per D19, the interactor now also holds a LintConfigLoader port (generic C: LintConfigLoader) used when command.rules is empty — the execute flow checks rules first, falls back to loading from config via the port, and fails closed if neither is available. The CatalogueLoader port (L: CatalogueLoader) is retained for external I/O. Generic over both L and C to avoid Arc<dyn Trait> boxing at this boundary.",
      "spec_refs": [
        {
