      "docs": "Errors returned by LintConfigLoader::load. MissingFile: the config file does not exist at the given path (fail-closed per OS-10 — no silent fallback). ParseError: the file exists but cannot be parsed as valid JSON or its structure is invalid. SchemaVersionMismatch: the config file schema_version field does not match the expected version — prevents silently misinterpreting a config written for a different schema.",
