      "methods": [],
      "module_path": "catalogue_lint_workflow",
      "docs": "Errors from the RunCatalogueLint use case. Modify from baseline: CatalogueLoad continues to wrap CatalogueLoaderError because the interactor still performs external catalogue loading; LintExecution wraps domain CatalogueLinterError from evaluate_catalogue_lint rather than an infrastructure CatalogueLinter port. InvalidLayer(String) carries the unknown layer id; InvalidRuleSpec(String) carries the rejection reason from domain constructor validation. ConfigMissing is returned when command.rules is empty and LintConfigLoader::load returns MissingFile — fail-closed behavior per OS-10 (no silent fallback to any preset). ConfigInvalid wraps LintConfigLoaderError for ParseError and SchemaVersionMismatch cases — the config file exists but cannot be loaded successfully.",
